  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Launched\u00a008/15/2017 2:59 CT (19:59 UTC)</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.1-TicketDelete\">Ticket Delete</h2><p>With the 1.13 release the ticket delete function\u00a0stopped\u00a0working properly. Ticket delete functionality is now\u00a0restored.\u00a0</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.1-QuickBooksUpdates\">QuickBooks Updates</h2><p>Improved settings screens for QuickBooks setup. Integration with several QuickBooks Online accounts (one per location) is now supported.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.1-Qsite-CustomerPortal\">Qsite - Customer Portal</h2><p>We improved the cache-busting for Qsite styling so that any new style changes are received automatically.</p><p>We fixed a few issues with the &quot;current&quot; logo that was displayed on the branding settings page for the Qsite Customer Portal logo.</p>",
